Comment: 50,0:23:53.04,0:23:53.08,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 50,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.30,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Morning, Uguisu.
Dialogue: 50,0:00:38.10,0:00:41.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, right! I can use magic now!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.17,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.47,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,We're going out to play, Uguisu!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:12.89,0:01:14.80,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 50,0:01:17.93,0:01:18.98,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,The city!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.12,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.83,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Fuu, you're up early for a Sunday.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.42,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Morning, Dad! I'm gonna go out to play!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.17,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Where to? A friend's house?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.55,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, Azuki!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.01,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Were you with big sis this whole time?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.47,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,She was.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.77,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,She's gotten attached to me.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.52,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.27,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's cute.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.94,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Good for you, Azuki!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.66,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Big sis, can I...?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.53,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.66,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Those fireworks last night...
Dialogue: 50,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.67,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.30,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,They sure were amazing though.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.84,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,They {\i1}were{\i0} amazing, weren't they?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.97,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Come eat breakfast, Fuu.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.01,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Okie-dokie!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.90,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You coming with, Azuki?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.57,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,She wants to stay home.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Then off I go!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.84,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Welcome in!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.84,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:56.78,0:05:02.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to go out into the city\Nwearing something pretty when I grew up!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,First off, I wanna try a crepe!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.25,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:07.25,0:05:10.75,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Because when I told Dad\NI wanted a crepe,
Dialogue: 50,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.58,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,he gave me a dorayaki instead!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.84,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,All because we run a confectionery.\NIsn't that unfair?!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.42,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.38,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,All of it!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.22,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Though I haven't had it before.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.36,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wowie!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.99,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.99,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,So crowded... Scary...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I gotta find somewhere to transform...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.75,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:53.75,0:05:57.42,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,No one can find out about my magic, right?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.05,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Right. Else you'll explode.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.88,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Y-You're kidding!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.51,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Then how should I...
Dialogue: 50,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.11,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.49,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,Yes! Would you like to try on some clothes?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.62,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I try on this dress?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.46,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,It might be a bit big for you...
Dialogue: 50,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.33,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.42,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'll grow into it in a sec!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.22,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Litto!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I like it!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Does it look good?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.45,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.28,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.12,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Can I buy this and keep it on?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.37,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,C-Certainly. You look great in it.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.13,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.46,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,Thank you for shopping!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.97,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,That worked perfectly!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.38,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,What a handful.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:26.38,0:07:30.47,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! I've always wanted to wear\Nmature clothes like this!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.97,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Let's go have some fun!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.36,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,One creamy crepe, please!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.49,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Time to dig in!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.04,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,You've got cream on your face.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.00,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Want to try it, Uguisu?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.29,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Take a big bite!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.60,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Are you okay staying behind?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:18.69,0:08:21.23,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,You must like being at home, huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.98,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,You're just like me.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.24,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Though it wasn't always this way...{similar phrasing ep 1 4:57}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:32.16,0:08:35.66,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Where's Fuu off playing right now?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.25,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I turned her invite to the pool down.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.84,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I just can't do it.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.51,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.60,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I should learn more about you.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.86,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Kabappy!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.36,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I want one...{trim line at keyframe?}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:16.87,0:09:17.70,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.33,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.67,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula...
Dialogue: 50,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.59,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Win the stuffie!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.22,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.26,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,You stink.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.39,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You're so useless, magic!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.60,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Why didn't it work?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.56,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,If you truly wish for it,\Nit'll come true.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.19,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,But I {\i1}did{\i0} truly want it!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:46.69,0:09:50.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Magic's a lot more worthless\Nthan I thought.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.49,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Aw man...
Dialogue: 50,0:09:53.49,0:09:56.24,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be able to do anything.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.29,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:05.67,0:10:09.92,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What's going on here?\NMy drink turned into a stuffie!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.17,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,That's your magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.55,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.85,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So the spell I cast before\Nonly just activated?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:16.89,0:10:20.56,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Though it looks a bit different\Nfrom Kabappy...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.65,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.34,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What should I do next?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:50.84,0:10:54.34,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I've basically done everything I wanted to...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.14,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything else.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.85,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What haven't I done yet?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.89,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey, Uguisu.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What should I do after this?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.15,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Go home?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.77,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:09.77,0:11:14.36,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I came out all this way.\NI gotta do more things!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.86,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:17.91,0:11:20.24,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I don't know. That's why I asked...
Dialogue: 50,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.95,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,I got nothing.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.29,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something fun to do...
Dialogue: 50,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.63,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 50,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.13,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,She's perfect!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.35,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Mind if I sit with you?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.77,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:43.77,0:11:44.68,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.06,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,So, listen.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.48,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.61,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Wanna be an idol?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.49,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,My name's Kandachi Toko.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:00.37,0:12:03.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Production Once More?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:03.20,0:12:06.87,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's my own agency.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.08,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What, you're the founder?!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.54,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.21,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It's fresh, so we don't have\Na lot of talent yet...
Dialogue: 50,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.47,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This is one of our performances.\NI'm an idol myself!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:18.47,0:12:21.14,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wow, you really are!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.76,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I have a dream.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.98,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I want to be recognized as a great idol by all!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:27.81,0:12:32.02,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Once I do that, I know I can change the world!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh really? Good luck with that!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.20,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,And I know I can do it with you on my side!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Please, I could never!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:43.20,0:12:47.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Only super cool people become idols, right?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.29,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,My grades are pretty average,
Dialogue: 50,0:12:50.29,0:12:53.09,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,and I always mess up my chores.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.59,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You have this curious charm about you, though.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.97,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Aw, you think so?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:59.97,0:13:03.26,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Though now that I talk to you,\Nyou also seem kind of childish.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.10,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But that contrast is just cute!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:06.72,0:13:10.35,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Becoming an idol will turn your life upside down.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.40,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You'll get to experience so many exciting things,
Dialogue: 50,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.48,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,and maybe catch the eye of a loved one.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.36,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.40,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:19.99,0:13:23.87,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,The moment I laid my eyes on you,\NI thought, "this is the one!"
Dialogue: 50,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.37,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,If we work together,\NI know things will start to shift.{何かが動く, similar to fuu's 何かが変わる in ep 1}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.04,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Will you do it?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.75,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 50,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.55,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I can do it?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.80,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know{\i0} you can!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:40.34,0:13:45.14,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Also, you'll get to eat\Na lot of yummy things as an idol!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:45.68,0:13:48.22,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,And wear all the cute clothes\Nyour heart desires!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.10,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You like the sound of that?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.06,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, I do!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.48,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I like your honesty.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.78,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Is this a good idea?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.61,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.24,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.21,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.09,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,The stage of our next performance...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.59,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Uh-huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.09,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Starring you.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:19.09,0:14:19.71,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.63,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I was actually supposed to perform,
Dialogue: 50,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.51,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,but you're perfect for this!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.01,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.56,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I messaged you about this before.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This girl is our agency's promising new idol!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.57,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Oh, right. You mentioned a change to the casting.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.90,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Pleased to work with you.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.82,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:41.82,0:14:45.28,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a minute! I haven't even...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.32,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:48.16,0:14:48.87,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.29,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lilly.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.63,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lilly?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.51,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Could use a bit more oomph...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.01,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Anything you like?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.55,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Like a favorite snack?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.89,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I guess konpeito?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.27,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Good, we'll roll with that.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.10,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Your stage name will be...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.60,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,CompatoLilly!{official spelling}
Dialogue: 50,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.86,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.03,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,It's time to go live.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.08,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Please get on standby.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.17,Default,MC,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.92,Default,MC,0,0,0,,It's time for the\NShibu-Yeahhh Teens Meeting
Dialogue: 50,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.67,Default,MC,0,0,0,,to get on the road!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.72,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no...{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.68,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I agreed to this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:15:46.68,0:15:49.76,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I have no idea what I'm doing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:15:51.89,0:15:56.81,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I mean, I can't go on stage!\NI'm not ready for this...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.23,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Relax. Just sing whatever you want.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:01.44,0:16:06.28,Default,MC,0,0,0,,Now, allow me to introduce\Nthe idol making her grand debut!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:06.28,0:16:08.45,Default,MC,0,0,0,,CompatoLilly!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:08.86,0:16:09.95,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.95,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Break a leg!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.63,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you, I'm Lilly!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.09,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I h-hope you enjoy...
Dialogue: 50,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.76,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Hey, not over there!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:24.76,0:16:25.96,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Move up front!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.34,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.97,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.52,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darn it, I messed up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.86,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.73,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew I wasn't cut out to be an idol...{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.53,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Relax! Now sing!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.95,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Big sis, I can't sing very good...
Dialogue: 50,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.34,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Relax!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.84,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Fuu, let's sing together!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.81,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, doing this was my decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:24.06,0:17:27.07,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may as well have fun doing it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:27.36,0:17:31.07,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like when I used to sing\Nwith my big sis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.25,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.17,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Pam pam power!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.60,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What is she doing...?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.98,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Let's get it on!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.26,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,What a crowd.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.59,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Looks like some concert.
Dialogue: 51,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.92,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I take off my sneakers, feeling I've grown{スニーカー脱いで少し背伸びな}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.17,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Bout to head out in my new fit{新しいコーデで歩きだそう}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:13.17,0:19:16.68,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Earrings dangling, lip gloss on{揺れるアクセと唇グロスオン}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:16.68,0:19:20.10,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Somehow dazzling even inside{なぜか心も輝くよ}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:20.10,0:19:23.48,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}It all seemed like a fairy tale on a screen{画面の中だけおとぎ話って}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:23.48,0:19:26.98,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Something far, far away I could never reach{そんなふうに遠く見えていた}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:26.98,0:19:30.40,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But I leap onto the crossing, perhaps I'll find my love{飛び込めスクランブル出会うもかもラブ}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:30.40,0:19:34.40,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And cast a spell on you{魔法振りかけて}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.57,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Sing with me
Dialogue: 51,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.99,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Su-Sugar Sugarly La Lu Sugarin'
Dialogue: 51,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.33,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll coat even your sighs in sugar{君のため息もシュガーでコーティング}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:42.33,0:19:45.41,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Even the same old bustling intersection{見慣れた雑踏交差点}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:45.41,0:19:49.17,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can become a stage with a touch of magic{ほらマジック　ステージに変わる}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.63,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Su-Sugar Sugarly La Lu Sugarin'
Dialogue: 51,0:19:52.63,0:19:56.13,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Every lost gaze, come to me{迷子の目線を全部ちょうだい}
Dialogue: 51,0:19:56.13,0:20:01.85,INS,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll stuff a balloon full of sparkly lights{キラキラだらけをバルーン詰め込んだら}
