Dialogue: 50,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.96,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\an8}President, I've found her.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.17,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's the one!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.49,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,That was crazy cool!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.01,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.51,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.85,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Did I do good?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.85,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Did you do good?! Look!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.27,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,All those people came to watch!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.69,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You did fantastic!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.07,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:56.07,0:20:59.28,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Your performance blew my expectations away!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:59.28,0:21:01.36,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It was so magical!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:01.91,0:21:05.37,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I could see the world changing\Nright in front of me!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:06.16,0:21:09.62,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Now that I have you,\NI think I can dream even greater than before.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.50,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,So let's keep at this together!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:14.88,0:21:19.13,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I appreciate all of that,\Nbut I don't know...
Dialogue: 50,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.64,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I messed up on stage,
Dialogue: 50,0:21:21.64,0:21:25.51,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,and I'm not sure if\NI really want to or not.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:25.81,0:21:29.52,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Then how about we go eat\Nsomething yummy like I promised?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:29.52,0:21:33.52,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Remember? I said you'd get\Nto eat a lot as an idol.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.28,Default,Fuu / Toko,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.70,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Shota, look, it's her!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.25,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,The girl on the stage!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:53.71,0:21:55.25,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This way, Lilly!
Dialogue: 50,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.73,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 50,0:22:20.32,0:22:21.82,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,want to do that too...
