Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.67,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Ooh, ooh, ooh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.67,0:01:35.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}You're my little buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.71,0:01:40.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Hey, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.96,0:01:40.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bubee, bubee, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.92,0:01:43.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}My heart is racing like crazy{ドキドキしている私}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.22,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}And right before my eyes{この目に映るのは}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.22,0:01:49.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Are the colors of a brand new world{新しい世界の色}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.47,0:01:50.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Woah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Stay with me today{今日もそばにいて}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.19,0:01:57.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}We'll walk hand in hand{君の手を取って行こう}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.19,0:02:00.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Dreaming of the place where we can become light{光に成れる場所に憧れて}
