Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:27.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Proof!){「proof！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}It's what binds us together{「それが 二つ 結ぶ絆だから」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:34.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(My dream!){「my dream！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I just wanna know what the future holds{「明日の扉の向こう期待しちゃう」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:38.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Alone!){「alone！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:42.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Even if the stars in a moonless sky{もしも月のない 空に星が}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Still twinkle{輝いても}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:45.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(No magic!){「no magic！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:49.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Even if the clouds in a sunless sky{もしも太陽がない 空の雲が}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Still drift{流れてても}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I feel so lonely{淋しそうに}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:56.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(I was always right beside you){『当たり前に隣に居た』}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I'm searching for you{君を探してる}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:02.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I'll frame a photo of us two and hang it up{二人映る 額縁(frame)Decorate！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Let's set things the way we want, the way we will, the way they are{思うがまま ワガまま ありのままに並べよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:10.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Take our chemistry, plus+, minus-, multiplied×, divided÷ by...{相性 Plus＋ Minus－ Multiply× Divide÷ by…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:10.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I love it every way{「全部好き」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Calling me, calling you{Calling me Calling you}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:15.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(And you){「＆you」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I want to walk up the stairs of the future with you{君と歩きたい 未来階段(stairs)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Lucky lucky shiny, our beating hearts dreamin' away{Lucky Lucky Shiny 二人の ときめきDreamin’}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:25.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}If there's clear skies tomorrow, everything will be okay{明日晴れなら 万事オーライ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Maybe I'm a bit sad and weak{ちょっとブルー Weakness}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:29.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(But I'm happy!){(but happy)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}But when I'm with you I feel safe{けど君が居るから Being saved}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}There's no such thing as wasted time{無駄な時間なんて無い}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Let's wait until the rain stops{雨上がる空をWaiting}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:39.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Check it out, look up at the sky{Check it out 見上げたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Courage is in two worlds, yeah, together now{Courage is in two worlds そう Together now}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:43.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Proof!){「proof！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}That's what binds us together{「それが 二つ 結ぶ絆だから」}
